OL,5, The former chief executive of S4C has  
OL,6, written to the UK government's culture 
OL,7, secretary saying the channel's chairman
OL,8, is the "embodiment" of a "culture of   
OL,9, fear, secrecy and excessive control".  
OL,11,FSian Doyle was sacked on Friday in a   
OL,12,F"difficult but unanimous decision" by  
OL,13,FS4C's independent board members.       
OL,15,FThe letter to the culture secretary    
OL,16,Fasks a series of questions about S4C   
OL,17,FChairman Rhodri Williams's behaviour.  
OL,19,FMs Doyle has not responded to requests 
OL,20,Ffor an interview.                      
